Metric: Monthly Recurring Revenue
Description: Total MRR from active subscriptions in the current billing cycle
Owner: finance-team
Tags: finance, saas, recurring

Source: subscriptions, payments

Given all records from subscriptions table
  And status is "active"
  And billing_date is within current calendar month

When we calculate
  Then sum the mrr column
  And exclude trial accounts
  And round to 2 decimal places

The result is "Monthly Recurring Revenue"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 12 hours
  Null rate on mrr must be less than 2%
  Null rate on status must be 0%
  Row count must not drop more than 10% day over day
  Row count of payments must not drop more than 15% week over week
  Value must be between 100,000 and 5,000,000
  Value must not change more than 30% month over month
